        <T> Function<T> newFunction(String functionId)
        Creates a new object that allows the execution of functions in the distributed system.
        Type Parameters:
        T - Type of result returned from the function. May differ from the key and values types of any involved regions.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        Function abstraction.
